data.description: Back on the Market!!! Inspection on the house is very good. Buyer financing fell through. NO CDD, LOW HOA AND NEW ROOF INSTALLED BEFORE CLOSING!!!  YOU GET TO PICK THE COLOR OF THE ROOF!  This is a great opportunity to purchase in the highly sought after community of Walden Lakes East in Plant City. Are you looking for a home with space this is it. Walking in the door you are greated with an open floor plan with ceramic tile through out. Property features bonus space with stone wood burning fire place, formal living room and dining space. Sky light makes for a bright space. Kitchen has black newer appliances, white cabinets with granite counter tops. Property has 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms, the master bedroom has a spacious walk-in closet with on suite bathroom. Master bath features a jacuzzi tub for a wonderful time of relaxation, walk-in shower and seperate closet for commode. French doors leading to a spacious screened lanai and a tool/storage room off the back of the home. The pie-shaped back yard is beautifully landscaped with tropical plants and trees. A portion of the back yard is maintained by the Hoa per easement of Walden Lakes East. Location is great close to shopping, hospital and restaurants.
